text:
藝文化（日本文化）
武藝，睿智的結晶，花藝，發揮構想，迸發出火花來，彩藝，彩蝶飛舞（血染雲，博彩）茶藝：茶道中的真蒂，酒藝，世界興起，品酩，波浪彈奏，愛情酒的潮流，時裝-strong，勢壯-著藝，酒神,Diony,創作：浪漫的詩篇-玫瑰與槍.舞勇，戰慄舞_世間的人，感到恐懼.刀藝`尖峰刀銳，紙鋒利，紙藝，弘藝，藝彩，棋藝：棋盤上，相互的步數，一步一步來，香之藝，禪藝,真道學，性禪學，Sex~性的藝術，Sex的魅力及引力,源源不絕地：創造力，精力旺盛，男兒性，男性～性器官，連發，直挺，男性的：魅力及引力，狂野不羈，女性的：魅力及引力，為她癡；為她狂，為她而瘋狂，女性：忘我的性愛，男性，猛刺，性興奮，野外性派對，革除：假道學，破除：假道學.料理藝術：司壽，延長壽命，存活·冰品，藝術之美，景觀藝術，徐徐的和風，藝術品宴，庭園藝術，和服美藝·飛迅Fashion，藝術造形，髮藝，代表，自我的髮藝，心響應，藝術建築，人類的瑰寶，極緻的：建築藝術，重要的：建築藝術，古典美藝，盆栽藝術，圖像藝術，人體藝術大展，弓箭之藝，書寫之藝，畫作之藝：春天的畫作，思情畫藝，藝術的哲學之道，揉和之藝，淡雅之藝的菓子，論，交易的藝術：藝者，歌樂，舞道，娛樂性；藝術性～藝之財-企業獨創：特有的藝術，藝術的功效，特別罕見，稀有的價值！藝術的效益；藝術的效力.妝典之藝，鍛鍊刀的藝術家，拔刀之藝，試斬刀，光之藝，展心，光景，開光，1品，藝術品，藝術品的魅力，至高無上的藝術品，1品中的1品，手刀劈，刀斬之藝，舞劍之藝"劍法之藝，盔甲武士之利，拳法之藝，兵法，藝術講演，兵形象水，水之流，匯集而成，奔流而至，沖擊，沖垮堤防，潰堤{Art的紛發氣}全新的，嶄新的：斬法之藝，神魂出鞘»斬除敗類（極利）…軍事作戰,駿馬-寶血馬-急速飆風的快感！對敵人，劈成兩半，弘廣的戰爭藝術！主宰，紛發出去，不斷繁演出來…
Great to see old friends and a great business establishment.

【會員故事 The story of our member】 Kafnu Taipei

北京出生、美國長大的Charles是一個標準的科技游牧民族（Digital Nomad），周遊世界各地的旅居生活已經四年了！

再次來到台北的他透過Google以及朋友介紹而來到Kafnu Taipei，並跟我們分享了關於他第一次愛上台灣的故事：
「當時在大安捷運站附近的居酒屋吃飯，點了一條烤魚，但這隻魚比一般的尺寸還要小，店家表示可以收我比較便宜的費用，問我願不願意。」他淺淺笑了，語帶一點激動地說：「他們明明可以照常收費的，卻還是主動給我折價了！」Charles非常感動，也從此愛上台灣的人情味。

被問到喜歡Kafnu的哪些地方，Charles回答「很喜歡這邊的社群多樣性，有各式各樣不同背景的人而且大家都很nice！另外特別喜歡Kafnu的社群經理們，大家總是介紹我這附近哪裡好吃、哪裡好玩，讓我能夠更深入的了解跟體驗台北。」

熱愛教育工作的Charles目前從事「產品專案管理課程」的線上講師，編排的課程翻譯成三種不同語言，在全球有分別來自140個國家、超過20,000位學生；除此之外，Charles還是一名瑜珈愛好者，目前定期在Kafnu
Taipei舉辦 #啤酒瑜珈、#紅酒瑜珈 課程，希望透過課程的推廣，讓大家跟他一樣徹底愛上瑜珈！

最後問到Charles「這次打算在台灣待多久？下一個國家要去哪？」
他只是笑笑地表示「我也不知道！」


Born in Beijing, raised in the States and now traveling and living the world for
over four years, Charles is the epitome of a digital nomad!

Arriving in Taipei yet again and referred to Kafnu by a friend, he shares his
thoughts" I like the diversity here. There is a bunch of people from different
backgrounds and they are nice! I also like the community managers since they
really point out things to go try and look around the area."

He also shared with us why he has fallen in love with Taiwan: "I went to an
Izakaya restaurant right next to the Daan MRT station, I ordered a fish and the
chef served me what I have ordered, after the fish came out, the chef told me
that because the fish I ordered is smaller than its normal size, so they were
gonna charge me less from the cheque, and asked "Is that OK?" With his eyes
squinted, Charles laughed, "They could have just charged me the normal price! I
think that one simple offer made me feel like the people here are really sincere
and made me fall in love with Taiwan immediately!" 

With a love to experience life, Charles is passionate and enjoys sharing his
knowledge with others. Currently, he has been teaching “Software Project
Management” through online courses and online communities for four years. The
programs are translated into 3 different languages with over 20,000 students
from over 140 countries. In addition, Charles is also a yoga instructor, he
hosts beer and wine yoga at Kafnu Taipei, in hopes of promoting the benefits of
yoga so more and more people can get involved and grow their passion for it.

Kafnu Taipei

【Kafnu at InnoVEX】 #Day2

 來讓我們更深入的介紹今年的 InnoVEX 有哪些內容吧！

 邁入第四年的InnoVEX 新創特展，本次吸引了24國約476組海內外新創團隊參展，其中荷蘭、韓國、日本等11國均設立了自己的國家館。

 此外場內還有多場不同主題的座談會供大家自由參加；另一個看點就是官方主辦的超熱血新創投案賽，讓各組新創團隊互相交流切磋並爭取優勝。

 
而本次展覽的主題圍繞在新創生態圈（StartupEcosystem）、運動科技（Sportstech）、物聯網（IoT）、智慧機械（SmartMachinery）、生物科技（Biotech）、人工智慧（AI）、區塊鏈（Blockchain）等最新創業科技議題。

 實際走入館內會發現除了最夯的人工智慧、區塊鍊等酷炫的產品之外，有越來越多的團隊開始注重醫療、健康、環保、減碳等議題上，例如台灣科技新創基地（Taiwan
Tech Arena）的展位你可以看見各式各樣健康醫療類型的新科技，像是：幹細胞的培養與應用、食物過敏源的調查裝置、通過加熱快速塑形的關節固定器；而環保議題
則有許多運用再生資源的環保產品、環境友善的農業革新技術或是奧迪（Audi）推出的新版電動汽車。

 來InnoVEX走一圈，你可以深刻的感受到人的生活正藉由科技，快速的朝著更好方向發展中，而台灣也努力成為其中舉足輕重的一員。
生在這個時代的我們很榮幸能夠參與並見證這些人類的里程碑，讓我們一起投身這波瘋狂的創新潮流之中吧！

 Featuring 467 startups from 24 countries; InnoVEX has seen a 20% growth from
last year and this will be the largest InnoVEX so far. 
It is estimated that over 20,000 visitors will visit InnoVEX, making the event
to be for ICT startups around the world. The forum will take place from May 29 –
31 in the InnoVEX Center Stage. 

 This year, the forum covers a wide range of topics: AI, Biotech, Blockchain,
IoT Application, Smart Machinery, Sports Tech, and Startup Ecosystem. In the
InnoVEX Forum, over 40 speakers from leading companies & accelerators around the
world will share their insights on the topics through keynote speeches and panel
discussions cover the topic with StartupEcosystem, Sportstech, IoT,
SmartMachinery, Biotech, AI & Blockchain. 

 It is exciting to see the pitching competition take place from the first day as
tomorrow will be the final round of the competition. Come visit us at Kafnu
Taipei, see who will be the winning team of 2019 InnoVEX Pitch Contest!

【會員故事 The story of our member】

進駐於Kafnu Taipei的團隊《 名廚 GreatChef
》，是一個專門提供給餐飲相關人士的媒體與社群，透過採訪各地廚師、報導全球餐飲相關資訊，曝光在《名廚》的平台上，讓無論是赫赫有名的大廚師，或是初出茅廬的年輕廚師，都能夠有一個學習與獲取新資訊的平台，同時也期望廚師們能夠分享自身的知識回饋給社群。

實際打開《名廚》的App可以發現許多不同背景的廚師們分享自己的食譜與研究，也可以看到許多餐飲職人的專訪、世界各大料理活動的採訪報導、最新的餐飲資訊等等豐富的內容。

「廚師就是一間餐廳的CTO（首席技術長），就是技術的核心。」名廚在台北的負責人Perry如此說道。「但是我們除了廚師圈之外，也希望其他生產者、美食評論家等餐飲相關的人事物能一起加入這個社群，進而讓整個餐飲生態的層次能夠提高。」

而詢問到為何選擇Kafnu
Taipei做為團隊的落腳處，負責人Perry直言「最喜歡這邊的空間，裝潢、氣氛、設備都讓人感到很舒適。」；身為編輯的Atomy表示「特別喜歡Kafnu的魚缸！非常療癒~」；而本身經營著粉專
深夜女子公寓的料理習作的Mokki也表示很喜歡Kafnu自由的空間規劃。

如果本身就是廚師或是在餐飲相關產業工作又或是對餐飲有興趣的人，絕對要來認識一下《名廚Great Chef》，裡面絕對能夠找到對你有幫助的資訊！

Greatchef team currently located at 10F #1002 office pod in Kafnu Taipei. 

 They are a chef focused social media platform featuring talented chefs around
the world and their best-plated work as to excite and inspire others. They are
dedicated to creating a place where all the dishes and culinary knowledge can be
shared and exchanged among chefs. 

 Greatchef's app is full with surprises, the contents include sharing of
recipes, discuss of develop new menus and adding new or trendy ingredients,
stories of F&B professionals and world class culinary events. 

 “The chef is a CTO of a restaurant” says Perry, the co-founder of Greatchef.
“We are expecting more people join our platform other than chefs. Farmers,
fishermen, food providers and critics can be part of this community and enhance
the overall F&B ecosystem.

 Other than the social media platform, Greatchef also host various event to
connect with local F&B community and foodies such as “diningout-taiwan” (Ye Tai
Xi) event. Focus on dining experiences at open air space from local Taiwan
talented chefs with local fresh ingredients. This event is aiming at the
connections between local food providers with Taiwan chefs.

 上週為了慶祝端午節，我們在每週三下午的會員專屬 #下午茶小聚 特地準備了應景的 #鹼粽
，獨特的風味讓許多外國會員吃下去之後露出狐疑的表情，但台灣孩子們倒是一顆接著一顆，一下子就一掃而空了🤤

 你吃過鹼粽嗎？ 你喜歡嗎？ 留言跟我們分享吧～

 Last week in celebration of the dragon boat festival🐲, Kafnu Taipei prepared a
very special Kansui dumpling (sweet rice dumpling) for members to enjoy!!
This local festive delicacy was popular amongst our local members and its unique
taste and scent were definitely a new flavor to our foreign friends! 

 Have you ever tried a Kansui dumpling in Taiwan? Let us know your thoughts!!

在Kafnu，我們不斷的嘗試提供更好的服務給予我們的會員以及社群！

 讓我們歡迎新加入的行政主廚Timothy
Lu和他的團隊，新夥伴將各位帶來全新的當代美式餐點，並且在接下來的兩週打造全新Kafnu餐酒館，歡迎大家隨時關注我們！

 並且邀請各位朋友們在 #10月26日 試營運開幕日一起來玩，與我們一同分享這份喜悅！

 Here at Kafnu, we are always aiming to better serve our members and our
community.
We are very excited to welcome our new Executive Chef Timothy Lu and his team.
The team aims to bring their contemporary American influenced cuisine to share
with our beloved members and guests.
Stay tuned and follow us for the next 2 weeks as we develop the new "Kafnu
Restaurant and Bar".
Looking forward to seeing you at our soft opening on Oct. 26th.

希望能夠得到更多被國際看見的機會，

 Kafnu Taipei也藉著這次參展的機會來跟大家近距離接觸，

如果你有來參加InnoVEX的話別忘了來找我們玩！

Interview with BLKSODA's Raymen Wu 
(中文請往下滑）

 K: How long have you been working from Kafnu?
R: 9 months.

 K: What does your team do? How does Kafnu facilitate your projects?
R: Our company is called BLKSODA, we provide marketing and PR services to
facilitate small to IPO companies to reach global medias and markets.

 https://www.blksoda.com

 Kafnu provides a creative environment and relaxed atmosphere to optimize my
team’s work efficiency. The design and setup also helps in some of our
commercial shoots. Also our clients loves to visit because of the overall vibe
and friendly staffs at Kafnu.

 K: What made you pick Kafnu in the first place? What do you like most about
Kafnu? What is your favorite space in Kafnu?
R: Initially selected Kafnu because of the liveliness atmosphere and the
interior design, the space is especially friendly for small teams. The location
is also another main reason for our selection, it is convenient business
district without being too commercial and too crowded, not to mention the close
proximity to the MRT.

 My favorite space in the whole building is the 7F lounge area.

 ---------

 K: To whom would you introduce Kafnu to and why?
R: I introduce Kafnu to all my friends, especially ones that has small startups.

 K: How would you describe Kafnu Taipei with one word?
R: Homework……actually “Home/work”

 K: BLKSODA團隊進駐 Kafnu 多久了？
R: 九個月。 六個月時，我們考慮過要不要搬到別的共享空間，結果發現真的是太喜歡 Kafnu 的人和環境。

 K: 你的團隊是做哪方面的？
Kafnu 又如何協助你的團隊達成目標 ?
R: 我們是BLKSODA，提供行銷和公關服務，以讓中小型至IPO團隊進入全球性媒體和市場。

 〔BLKSODA官網〕https://www.blksoda.com

 Kafnu 提供了一個新奇的空間和舒適的環境，讓我們效率總是在最佳狀態。
這裡的設計和格局也很適合讓我們做一些拍攝，更不用說我們的客戶也很喜歡來，他們喜歡這裡的整體氛圍，也覺得Kafnu的人都很棒。

 K: 當初為什麼選擇Kafnu？
你最喜歡Kafnu的哪一點？
大樓所有的空間中，你最喜歡哪一層？
R: 最初選擇Kafnu是因為這裡陽光的氣息，還有室內的設計。 這裡非常適合小型團隊。 
另一個要點是地點和交通，Kafnu在便利的商業區，但這區的商業氣息不重，也不至於太擁擠，離捷運也很近。

 整棟大樓裡，我個人最喜歡7樓交誼廳。

 K: 你會跟誰推薦Kafnu？
為什麼推薦？
R: 跟我所有的朋友。
尤其是那些有小型新創公司的。

 K: 如果只能選一個英文字，你會怎麼形容Kafnu？
R: Homework…… 開玩笑的，我是指在這裡工作就像在家一樣。

【Chanifit薔非呼吸療癒：香氛冥想的平衡與美麗】

 你知道呼吸也需要探索跟引導嗎？
經常性失眠 / 精神壓力大 / 負面情緒徘徊不去
該怎麼處理和釋放這些情緒呢？

 其實，呼吸是一把通往祥和的鑰匙
透過冥想讓交感神經達到平衡，提升覺察力
結合天然香氛的能量，緩解憂鬱和焦慮
平衡你的自律神經，找回遺失的自癒能力
最終與內在的你產生聯繫

 [ 活動大綱 ]
・深度舒壓冥想
・生命能量呼吸法練習（Pranayama）
・芳療101：對於身體與情緒的療癒
・芳香按摩：讓芳療師帶領你的雙手療癒自己
・愛的覺察練習
・100%現打蔬果汁／無酒精熱紅酒 試飲
・法式沙龍香水吧：客製香水迷你體驗
（參加者小禮：薔非NO.83淡香水2ml 一份）

活動地點：Kafnu Taipei 12F
